{"type":null,"faqId":46052,"title":"为什么天气信息不准确","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3576389in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:1.3784722in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>进入“天气”界面，下拉界面，更新天气。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170460\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>在更新天气之前，请确保手机已经连接移动网络或 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>若更新成功后，天气信息仍然不准确，可能是该天气应用的数据信息尚未更新，请稍后再试。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>下载其他类似的天气应用，查看信息是否准确。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170461\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>应用提供的天气数据无法达到完全准确，请以气象局发布的信息为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1832","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444375611000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"fi